{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香与神水宫女弟子宫南燕在船上对话，分析天一神水失窃案。楚留香推断盗水者必有神水宫内部人员相助，宫南燕最终透露宫中曾有一名少女因怀孕羞愤自杀。宫南燕给楚留香一个月期限查出真相，临走前告知自己名叫宫南燕。其后李红袖、宋甜儿与楚留香玩笑打趣。苏蓉蓉与楚留香商议对策，决定苏蓉蓉前往神水宫找其表姑打听消息，楚留香则前往济南调查朱砂掌门下弟子。楚留香在船舱的秘密六面镜室中挑选伪装身份，拒绝了山西钱庄老板马百万的身份，选择了关外采参帮瓢把子张啸林的身份。随后场景转至济南快意堂赌场——朱砂帮开设的赌局，介绍了其主管冷秋魂。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "冷姑娘，你若想将这件事谜底揭穿，就必须信任我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我不姓冷。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "那么，我该叫你什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就叫我冷姑娘吧!",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "第一，我们先要研究的是，那'天一神水'既不能换取财富，也不能助长武功，他为什么要偷呢?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这该问你才是。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "那'天一神水'惟一的用处，就是害人，而且不知不觉的将人害死，他费了许多力气，来偷这'天一神水'，显然只有一个原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这原因已足够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "由此点我们便可以断定'他'所要害的人，必然不是普通毒药所能害死的，也不是'他'自己的力量所能杀死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，否则'他'又何必冒险盗水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "但他若是真的能自'神水宫'将水盗去，世上还有几个他杀不死的人?能自'神水宫'中盗水，那要像你这等身手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "由此可见，'他'盗取神水，定有人在暗中相助。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你的意思是在说谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "神水失窃以后，你们宫中可有人失踪?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "原来你的意思是说本宫弟子有人在暗中助'他'盗水，所以盗走了神水之后，自己也畏罪潜逃了，是么?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "这难道不可能?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "自然可能，只可惜数十年来本宫的弟子却从无一人逃走，更绝不会有人失踪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "神水失窃以后，你们宫里难道什么事都没有发生么?譬如说，是不是有人自杀而死……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎会知道?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "的确有人自杀而死，是么?她为什么自杀的?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "本宫中的事，也是你随便问得的么?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "冷姑娘，这件事你一定得告诉我，只因这件事就是关键，你……你一定得相信我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她是个可爱的女孩子，既美丽，又多情，年纪也最轻，她……她既已死了，我不能再说她……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "她是不是因为有了身孕，自觉无颜见人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "这就对了，她一定是已被'他'骗去了身子，然后，又在'他'胁迫之下，盗出了神水，但'他'却没有遵守诺言将她带走，所以她只有死这一条路!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "住口!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "这本是千古以来，多情的少女们都难免遭遇到的悲惨命运，你与其为她伤心，倒不如设法找到'他'，为她报仇。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "要怎样才能找出'他'来?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "她临死之前，可曾说了什么话?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她只说……她对不起肚里的孩子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "在这种情况下，她为何不肯说出'他'是谁，仍然深怕别人伤害到'他'……唉!'他'究竟有什么魔力，竟能令少女为'他'如此痴情?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她的确从来没有提起过'他'。她根本从未提起过任何男人，我们实在做梦也想不到这种事会发生在她身上。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "平时，她有没有相识的男子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她几乎从来没有和男人讲过话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "怪事，今天怎会有许多怪事……五个素不相关的人，竟会在同一时间里死在一个地方!'神水宫'中的神水，竟会神秘的被窃!一个端庄淑静，从不与男人说话的少女，竟会有了身孕，而这三件事看起来也绝不会有什么关系的，竟偏偏又纠缠到一起……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种事，谁能解释?",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为了你自己，你必须将这谜底揭开。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "但线索呢……我几乎完全没有线索。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "线索必定有的，你自己找出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我给你一个月的时间，你若找不出来，神水宫就要来找你!",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你为何要转过身去?难道你面对着我时，就说不出这么不讲理的话?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我的名字叫宫南燕。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一个月后，你只怕就不会再觉得她美了，尤其当她的剑抵住你脖子的时候……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "她不用剑的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她用什么?菜刀?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "她用的是菜碗。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "菜碗?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "不用莱碗，怎么能接得住打翻了的醋瓶子?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你不能得罪她，她比宫南燕厉害得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "哦!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "宫南燕最多不过是'神水宫'弟子，但我们的李红袖姑娘，却是'神醋宫'的掌门人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "小鬼，你要不要命?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "蓉姐，救命呀!'神醋宫'的掌门人好厉害哟……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你现在想怎么办呢?",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "到现在为止，的确还没有丝毫线索可寻，但现在我们总算已知道'他'，必定是个美男子，否则那少女怎会对'他'如此痴心?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "女孩子并不一定喜欢英俊的男人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "以你想，'他'会是怎么样的一个人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他必定很会说话，很聪明，很会讨女孩子的欢心，也必定风流得很，年轻的女孩子，对这种男人是永远无法抵抗的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "但这样的男人，能进得了神水宫么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这种男人入了神水宫，只怕是不能活着出来了……世上能活着走出神水宫的男人，只怕根本没有几个。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "所以，我不得不求你做件事了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可是要我到神水宫去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "我……我只担心你的身子。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你以为我真的弱不禁风?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "不知道你能不能找着你表姑，问清楚平日究竟有些什么男人能进出神水宫?再问她那死了的女孩子究竟是怎么样一个人?平日喜欢做些什么事?最好能找出这女孩的遗物，她若有书信留下，那就太好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "天一亮，我就动身。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "只是你……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要说的话，我已知道了……我走了后，你呢?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "七天后，我在济南大明湖边的风雨亭上等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "济南?那岂非朱砂掌一派的根据地?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "海南派、七星帮，都离此太远，札木合更是远自关外而来，我惟有希望能自朱砂掌门下弟子口中，打听出一些消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你可得分外小心，他们若知道是你……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "他们虽然恨我，但还是拿我没法子的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "盗帅夜留香，销魂不知在何方?",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可是又要我为你在四方留香?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "对了，你一路上，不妨为我留下些香迹，让别人永远也摸不透我的行踪究竟在哪里，更不会想到我已到了济南。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你……你这次又想以什么身份出现呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "朱砂掌门下，大多是富家子弟，我若要他们信任我，敬重我，惟一的法子，就是装得比他们更豪阔。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要的只怕是六十三号?也可能是一百十三号?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "这号码对么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "大概不会错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "但看这衣服，就不像豪富穿的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "济南城中的行商，最殷实的只有两种，一种就是山西钱庄的大老板，而山西老板舍得穿这种衣服，已经算很大方的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "对了，我竟忘了山西人的银子大多都是用药水煮过的，有时我在奇怪，他们存下那么多银子，是为着什么呢?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "你若要我扮成这个样子，倒不如杀了我算了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是你自己叫我将每种典型人物的资料都准备一份的，连叫化子你都扮过，为什么就不能……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "我宁可做叫化子，也不愿当这种大老板。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么，你再瞧瞧一百十三号。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "来往济南城的，除了山西钱庄老板外，最豪阔的就是关外长白山一带，采参帮的瓢把子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "这看来想必有趣得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "有趣，果然有趣极了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我就知道一定合你意的，但不管怎样，你还是得带着那个箱子，我替你将三号、七号、二十八号、四十号都准备在箱子里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "好，从现在开始，我就做几天张啸林吧!",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    }
